 "remarks": "Welcome to this spacious 2-bedroom, 2.5-bath townhouse in the desirable Kingswood condominium community, offering the perfect blend of privacy, convenience, and commuter-friendly living. Ideally located near the Merritt 7 train station, the Norwalk River Valley Trail, shopping, dining, and major highways, this home makes everyday living effortless. The main level features an inviting living room with a cozy fireplace, a dining area ideal for entertaining, and a functional layout that flows comfortably throughout. Upstairs, you&apos;ll find two generously sized bedrooms, each offering comfort and ample closet space, along with two full bathrooms. The lower level provides exceptional versatility with interior access from the built-in garage and a flexible room-perfect for a home office, fitness area, hobby room, or additional storage. Step outside to the private walk-out patio, an ideal spot to relax or enjoy outdoor dining. Whether you&apos;re a first-time home owner, downsizing, or looking for a convenient commuter location, this well-maintained townhouse offers comfort, flexibility, and an outstanding location.",
